1
00:00:17,567 --> 00:00:19,067
So return to--

2
00:00:22,650 --> 00:00:24,108
[NAOFUMI]
What the hell are you doing?!

3
00:00:24,192 --> 00:00:25,483
Curse you!

4
00:00:25,567 --> 00:00:27,942
How dare you take the royal
Princess Melty hostage!

5
00:00:28,025 --> 00:00:29,692
I'm not taking anybody hostage!

6
00:00:29,775 --> 00:00:30,567
You're a liar!

7
00:00:30,650 --> 00:00:32,567
Fellow knights, justice is ours!

8
00:00:32,650 --> 00:00:34,567
Let's destroy this
Devil of the Shield!

9
00:00:34,650 --> 00:00:36,192
[KNIGHTS yell]

10
00:00:36,275 --> 00:00:39,233
Terrific, so now
I've become a devil, huh?

11
00:00:39,317 --> 00:00:41,108
Raphtalia! Filo!

12
00:00:44,650 --> 00:00:47,775
[yells]

13
00:00:50,692 --> 00:00:52,067
[giggles]

14
00:01:10,108 --> 00:01:11,275
Full retreat!

15
00:01:11,358 --> 00:01:12,358
[KNIGHTS yell]

16
00:01:12,442 --> 00:01:14,067
[KNIGHT 13A]
Run away!

17
00:01:16,358 --> 00:01:17,817
Can we chase them down?

18
00:01:17,900 --> 00:01:19,108
Nah.

19
00:01:19,983 --> 00:01:22,692
Mel, are you hurt anywhere?

20
00:01:25,775 --> 00:01:27,192
<i>Now or Never</i>

